props.header: We’re bringing our vision of the future on the road! Attend one of our regional events to learn how 2O36 is making a difference for Emory, your city, and the world.
props.text:
Enjoy an unforgettable evening of food, libations, connection, and inspiration with local Emory alumni, parents, and friends. Hear from a diverse panel of Emory leaders as they share the progress 2O36 is making for students and our shared future. You’ll come away with exclusive insight into the campaign’s signature themes, including student flourishing, A.I. humanity, cancer, and brain health.

Regional events are free to attend, but registration is required using the links below.* Business or cocktail attire is recommended.
